"Open your eyes, Guardian!": "Your end has not yet come! I will not let it!"
"The bonds you have forged are the answer!"
"This power you gave me... It was to save everyone..."
"I still haven't done anything with you! I haven't had the chance to be a normal girl!"
"If we leave things... There might still be a future ahead. But I... I don't want that!"
"I want to see the future with you!"
"Let us save our thanks for after we have taken care of that thing."
"...The overwhelming darkness we removed from you. Even without a host, it's still here..."
"It is the [Profound Darkness] born during the era of the Photoners. That darkness is its root. A pure desire to destroy."
"With both its destination and vessel lost, it has become power incarnate..."
"...We can't just leave it like this... I won't let anyone else become a sacrifice, ever again!"

"All that lives...
All that has ever lived...
All their wishes are gathering here."

"They're becoming a light to purify the darkness...
A Great Light..."
"The power of all living beings has gathered here. All that ever was has led to this."
"And from here, they will begin. The memories of a new universe."
"The bonds you have forged... They have all gathered here."
